content.title: Kuraba interface y'ubushobozi
content.howToUseTooltip:
Aha hepfo hariho ibimenyetso vy'iyi node ishobora gukoreshwa mu guhitamwo ibikorwa, nk'ugukanda, kwuzuza inyandiko, n'ibindi.

Agaciro k'ibiranga gashobora gusubirwamwo kuri paji ya app. Niwaba uhuye n’ibintu bibiri, ndagusavye ushiremwo ibindi bintu kugira ngo umenye ubudasa.

Ijambo ritukura ryerekana ko agaciro k’ibiranga gasubirwamwo, ijambo ry’icatsi kibisi ryerekana ko agaciro k’ibiranga kadasanzwe mu gushaka kuri paji ubu, kandi ijambo ryirabura ryerekana ko ata kugereranya.
content.otherNodesSummary: Ibindi bice biri muri iki kibanza
